ng 容器</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-markdown" data-language="markdown"><code class="language-markdown">:::warningWarning!!!:::</code></pre><div class="custom-quote warning"><span class="custom-quote-svg"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" data-reactroot=""><path fill="" d="M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z" undefined="1"></path><path stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke-width="2" stroke="" d="M12 8V13"></path><path stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke-width="2" stroke="" d="M12 15.99V16.01"></path></svg></span><p class="custom-quote-title">注意</p><p>Warning!!!</p></div><h3 id="Danger-容器"><a href="#Danger-容器" class="headerlink" title="Danger 容器"></a>Danger 容器</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-markdown" data-language="markdown"><code class="language-markdown">:::dangerDanger!!!:::</code></pre><div class="custom-quote danger"><span class="custom-quote-svg"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" data-reactroot=""><path fill="" d="M19.76 5.23C15.84 5.23 12 2 12 2C12 2 8.15996 5.23 4.23996 5.23C4.23996 5.23 1.86996 16.99 12 22C22.13 16.99 19.76 5.23 19.76 5.23Z" undefined="1"></path><path stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke-width="2" stroke="" d="M12 8V13"></path><path stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke-width="2" stroke="" d